@jontutoring @amrakunj @jo_ask You can ask the PM. He never answers a question in depth.
Worse he doesn't know his reply from yesterday and makes up a new one he things fits best.
He is a prime example described in Harry G. Frankfurt's book "On Bullshit". Read it. It is mind opening.

@jontutoring @amrakunj @jo_ask Everyone breaths a sigh of relief when a loved one is protected with a vaccine, regardless of nationality.
But the ‘if you don’t like it, move’ attitude is a bit unfair.
Most people who want to, can’t move abroad any more.
